Elastic Block Store
    + EC2 and EBS should be in same region

    + When you terminate a EC2, only root volume is deleted, all additional volumes will not be deleted

    + Delete on Termination only enabled for Root Volume

    Storage Comparison
    URL - https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ebs/latest/userguide/ebs-volume-types.html

    GP3 - GP2 - iO2 - iO1 - 

    What is Instance Store /(Kind of Cache/Swap storage) - once EC2 restarted, Data stored in Instance Store will be erased

    